nodes.text: Duuba the Magnanimous was an up-and-coming Hutt of the Hutt Cartel in 3626 BBY. He and his rival Gaboorga organized the charitable event called the Feast of Prosperity, to restore the Cartel's reputation and improve their own standings. However, Gaboorga and Duuba had conflicting interests and so enlisted the help of others to undermine each other.
The Hutt Duuba is featured in the update 6.1.4 to the Onslaught expansion of the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, as part of the "The Feast of Prosperity" anual event.
